{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2544178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一棵树是枣树，另一棵也是枣树🤣", "timestamp": 1632031753, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "wc", "timestamp": 1632031864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544190, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "高中数学全忘了", "timestamp": 1632031893, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544192, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学过概统就能做吧", "timestamp": 1632031899, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可见高中讲概率论的重要性", "timestamp": 1632031942, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544197, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "经典高中数学题", "timestamp": 1632031968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544187, "tag": null, "text": "诶，我概统全忘了，这不是独立事件嘛？是不是1/2？", "timestamp": 1632032092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544217, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "条件概率？1/3？", "timestamp": 1632032154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544226, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544195, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 如果是独立事件的话，表述应该为：第一个出生的孩子是女孩，求问第二个出生的孩子是女孩的概率", "timestamp": 1632032237, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544231, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544226, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 哦哦你说的有道理", "timestamp": 1632032265, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544232, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "条件概率的重要性", "timestamp": 1632032269, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如何理解“其中一个”，如果告诉我大孩子是女，那小孩子是女的概率为1/2；如果告诉我至少有一个是女，那就是1/3", "timestamp": 1632032330, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544240, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其中一个是女孩，有两种理解。\n1. 在两个孩子中，存在一个女孩。\n2. 在两个孩子中，某某某是女孩。", "timestamp": 1632032347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544244, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我个人读下来第一感觉是第一种解释。但是如果理解为第二种也无可厚非。", "timestamp": 1632032386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544267, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544244, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 哪有第1种理解，题目问了另一个孩子，那就是相对的原本那个是女孩。只能说第2种理解", "timestamp": 1632032597, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544289, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544267, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 自然语言的话确实有不确定性，我承认有人的第一感觉是第二种理解没毛病。但如果你认为第一种理解不存在的话就有点主观了，事实上G和I看他们的回复也应该是认为第一种。", "timestamp": 1632032837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544267, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 至少我认为这个题目出在数学吧里面，明显只是为了利用模糊的表述来引战的。", "timestamp": 1632032918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544304, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544297, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 我觉得jason的意思应该也明确的。", "timestamp": 1632032985, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 所以概率题必须要非常严格的表述才行，比如很经典的”在圆里随机取一个点”，也是因为文字表述不清引起误会。", "timestamp": 1632033064, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "语文题，和概率没关系，下一个", "timestamp": 1632033715, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544357, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 485854, "reply_to": 2544267, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 这么说吧，如果把\"其中一个\"英语翻译为“one of them\"，你应该就能理解为什么有人认为是1/3了。", "timestamp": 1632033738, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 485854, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "数学吧经典题目之3：\n已知你朋友家有两个孩子。现在他告诉你其中一个是女孩，问另一个孩子也是女孩的概率是多少？", "timestamp": 1632031573, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632033739, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"1/2": 147, "1/3": 150, "1/4": 8, "🍉/其它/题目描述不清": 76}, "vote_options": ["1/2", "1/3", "1/4", "🍉/其它/题目描述不清"]}}}